msgid ""
"\n"
"        <p>You can align images, videos, blockquotes and so on to "
"the left, right or center. Examples:</p>\n"
"        <ul>\n"
"          "
"<li>Align an image to the left: <code>&lt;img src=\"\" "
"data-align=\"left\" /&gt;</code></li>\n"
"          <li>Align an image "
"to the center: <code>&lt;img src=\"\" data-align=\"center\" "
"/&gt;</code></li>\n"
"          <li>Align an image to the right: "
"<code>&lt;img src=\"\" data-align=\"right\" /&gt;</code></li>\n"
"       "
"   <li>… and you can apply this to other elements as well: "
"<code>&lt;video src=\"\" data-align=\"center\" /&gt;</code></li>\n"
"    "
"    </ul>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Obrázky, videá, citácie a podobne môžete zarovnať doľava, "
"doprava alebo na stred. Príklady:</p>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"  <li>Zarovnanie "
"obrázka doľava: <code>&lt;img src=\"\" data-align=\"left\" "
"/&gt;</code></li>\n"
"  <li>Zarovnanie obrázka na stred: <code>&lt;img "
"src=\"\" data-align=\"center\" /&gt;</code></li>\n"
"  <li>Zarovnanie "
"obrázka doprava: <code>&lt;img src=\"\" data-align=\"right\" "
"/&gt;</code></li>\n"
"  <li>… a toto môžete použiť aj pre iné "
"prvky: <code>&lt;video src=\"\" data-align=\"center\" "
"/&gt;</code></li>\n"
"</ul>"

msgid "Align images"
msgstr "Zarovnať obrázky"

msgid ""
"Uses a <code>data-align</code> attribute on <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> "
"tags to align images."
msgstr ""
"Používa atribút <code>data-align</code> na <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> "
"značkách na zarovnanie obrázkov."

msgid ""
"\n"
"        <p>You can caption images, videos, blockquotes, and so on. "
"Examples:</p>\n"
"        <ul>\n"
"            <li><code>&lt;img src=\"\" "
"data-caption=\"This is a caption\" /&gt;</code></li>\n"
"            "
"<li><code>&lt;video src=\"\" data-caption=\"The Drupal Dance\" "
"/&gt;</code></li>\n"
"            <li><code>&lt;blockquote "
"data-caption=\"Dries Buytaert\"&gt;Drupal is "
"awesome!&lt;/blockquote&gt;</code></li>\n"
"            "
"<li><code>&lt;code data-caption=\"Hello world in "
"JavaScript.\"&gt;alert(\"Hello world!\");&lt;/code&gt;</code></li>\n"
"  "
"      </ul>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Môžete pridávať popisky k obrázkom, videám, citáciám a "
"podobne. Príklady:</p>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"    <li><code>&lt;img src=\"\" "
"data-caption=\"Toto je popis\" /&gt;</code></li>\n"
"    "
"<li><code>&lt;video src=\"\" data-caption=\"Drupal Dance\" "
"/&gt;</code></li>\n"
"    <li><code>&lt;blockquote data-caption=\"Dries "
"Buytaert\"&gt;Drupal je úžasný!&lt;/blockquote&gt;</code></li>\n"
"   "
" <li><code>&lt;code data-caption=\"Hello world v "
"JavaScripte.\"&gt;alert(\"Hello "
"world!\");&lt;/code&gt;</code></li>\n"
"</ul>"

msgid "Caption images"
msgstr "Popisky obrázkov"

msgid ""
"Uses a <code>data-caption</code> attribute on <code>&lt;img&gt;</code> "
"tags to caption images."
msgstr ""
"Používa atribút <code>data-caption</code> na značkách "
"<code>&lt;img&gt;</code> na popisovanie obrázkov."

