"Drush was unable to download the colorbox library from @remote. "
"@exception"
msgstr "Drush nedokázal stiahnuť knižnicu colorbox z @remote. @exception"

msgid "Error: unable to unzip colorbox file."
msgstr "Chyba: nepodarilo sa rozbaliť súbor colorbox."

